    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed in mint condition, and it absolutely earns that designation. The exterior is immaculate \u2014 the paint retains its original deep gloss with zero fading, chips, or scratches, and every panel is straight and true. The interior is equally pristine, with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim pieces, and all electronics and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, no unusual noises, and strong, confident performance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally cared for and shows like new \u2014 buyers who inspect it in person will not be disappointed. A full inspection is welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 47500.0,
