      "description": "Looking for the most affordable way to get rolling? This budget-friendly vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it shows noticeable wear inside and out, with some body damage and a well-used interior. Mechanically it can still get you from point A to point B, making it a candidate for a handy buyer looking for a project or a super-low-cost commuter. Perfect for someone who's mechanically inclined or just needs basic transportation without breaking the bank!",
