    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\u2728 Stunning Mint Condition \u2014 The One You've Been Waiting For! \u2728 This vehicle is in genuine mint condition, and it absolutely shows! The exterior boasts a brilliant, flawless finish with no scratches, dings, or blemishes to speak of. Step inside and you'll find an immaculate interior \u2014 clean, fresh, and feeling just like new. The mechanical components are in excellent shape, running smoothly and reliably. If you're looking for a vehicle that truly stands out from the crowd without the new-car price tag, this is your opportunity. Come see it for yourself \u2014 we're confident you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\ud83d\udcab",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a fair-condition car. Buyers should expect a car that is functional and drivable, but shows clear signs of wear and age throughout. The exterior has visible scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading in several areas \u2014 nothing catastrophic, but certainly not pristine. The interior shows moderate wear on the seats, dashboard, and trim, consistent with years of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though some components may be showing their age and could benefit from attention in the near future \u2014 buyers should budget for potential maintenance or repairs. This is a solid option for someone looking for basic, reliable transportation who doesn't mind putting in a little work or accepting cosmetic imperfections. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
